MATCH_TOOL: Bash
MATCH_PATTERN: git commit
ADVISORY: |
  Pre-commit: check for stale untracked artifacts (root *.png, **/test-results/, **/playwright-report/) — clean up or gitignore.
KILL_CONDITION: |
  When the guardian gains a Bash-side diff/predicate gate, this rule's
  noise floor will drop to ~zero and the advisory can be re-expanded with
  detail.
